  physical_appearance: The image shows a photograph with colour. It has a black frame and its border is white in colour. A set of railroad and a traffic light to the left of the photograph can be seen. The train has more than one carriage attached to it and it has two rows of windows on its side. There are a number of different colours which are only on the body of the locomotive
 while the rest of the photograph is in monochrome. There are colourful images of butterflies and flora that are coloured on the body of the locomotive.
